docs/codex-audio-investigation-brief.md:17:Random audio clicks/pops during music playback. Not rhythmic, not correlated with note attacks. Happens unpredictably — sometimes every 30 seconds, sometimes minutes apart. The music is generative ambient played through SuperCollider via PipeWire.
